WEBVTT

01:37.840 --> 01:41.060
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.120 --> 01:43.960
[Episode 36]

01:51.539 --> 01:52.120
Those two people

01:52.120 --> 01:55.380
are probably going to
fight it out in the sales department.

01:55.960 --> 01:57.740
Luckily, it has nothing to do
with our department.

01:57.740 --> 02:00.200
How come
they're not afraid to say anything?

02:00.390 --> 02:01.240
Listen.

02:01.790 --> 02:03.840
Now that
he has done something like this today,

02:03.840 --> 02:05.200
everyone in the meeting room

02:05.200 --> 02:07.060
knows exactly what he wants to do.

02:07.310 --> 02:08.430
When did Lu Zhenzhen

02:08.430 --> 02:10.160
get connected with Wei Siyuan?

02:11.450 --> 02:12.960
Between the vice director and the manager,

02:12.960 --> 02:15.210
there's just a difference in the titles.

02:15.210 --> 02:17.180
If Wei Siyuan wants it,
just let him have it.

02:17.180 --> 02:18.150
Tell Meng Jie

02:18.170 --> 02:20.480
Xu Miyu is the person
in charge of the bidding meeting,

02:20.480 --> 02:22.260
and all implementation details
must be checked by her.

02:22.260 --> 02:24.030
Don't let Lu Zhenzhen interfere.

02:24.030 --> 02:26.170
Leave the rest to Meng Jie
to handle by herself.

02:26.170 --> 02:27.510
She's quite experienced in the workplace.

02:27.510 --> 02:28.910
She knows the best how to deal with it.

02:28.910 --> 02:30.270
Okay. I'll tell her.

02:30.670 --> 02:31.360
Also,

02:32.240 --> 02:33.210
tell Miyu

02:34.010 --> 02:34.910
to be careful with everything.

02:34.910 --> 02:37.910
So the issues between you two
haven't been solved yet?

02:56.710 --> 02:58.570
Mr. Wei, what are your plans next?

03:00.300 --> 03:01.760
Now Ji Feng

03:01.780 --> 03:03.160
is clearly betting everything

03:03.160 --> 03:05.500
on the bidding meeting.

03:05.530 --> 03:08.330
And this time,
the sales department is the main focus.

03:08.330 --> 03:09.840
At this critical juncture,

03:09.840 --> 03:11.800
if he dares to use a newbie,

03:11.820 --> 03:13.220
then he'd better be prepared to fail.

03:13.220 --> 03:14.370
Don't forget that

03:14.800 --> 03:17.030
Xu Miyu is still in the sales department.

03:17.030 --> 03:17.840
That's right.

03:18.840 --> 03:20.190
So what's your plan?

03:20.780 --> 03:21.890
There's no rush.

03:23.520 --> 03:25.320
They are on high alert right now.

03:25.910 --> 03:28.560
When all the bidding companies
have checked in,

03:28.560 --> 03:30.610
and they're so busy receiving the guests,

03:30.610 --> 03:31.960
won't our chance come?

03:39.460 --> 03:41.670
Mr. Wei, I know that although this time,

03:41.690 --> 03:44.180
you only gave me
the position of vice director,

03:44.180 --> 03:46.640
you showed me a lot of respect
at the meeting.

03:47.020 --> 03:49.440
I will definitely find a way to help you.

04:00.280 --> 04:01.080
Miyu.

04:06.970 --> 04:07.960
Why are you here?

04:07.990 --> 04:09.050
What's the matter?

04:12.430 --> 04:13.280
Miyu.

04:14.520 --> 04:15.890
Our whole family

04:16.720 --> 04:18.160
has let you down.

04:20.510 --> 04:22.240
Don't talk about these things.

04:22.400 --> 04:24.380
What's the matter exactly?

04:25.930 --> 04:26.890
Yucheng...

04:28.870 --> 04:30.160
is sick.

04:30.890 --> 04:31.720
I know.

04:35.510 --> 04:37.440
He has undergone a major operation

04:38.390 --> 04:40.450
and several rounds of chemotherapy.

04:41.000 --> 04:42.240
Now suddenly,

04:44.890 --> 04:47.320
he wants to give up the treatment.

04:47.170 --> 04:51.930
[Welcome to Purong Hotel]

04:47.560 --> 04:48.360
He refuses to take his medicine.

04:48.360 --> 04:49.690
Nor is he willing to eat.

04:50.150 --> 04:52.050
He also refuses to
let the nurses give him IVs.

04:52.050 --> 04:55.250
No matter how I tried to persuade him,
he wouldn't listen.

04:55.360 --> 04:57.370
This is such a precious human life.

04:57.570 --> 04:59.780
Why doesn't he want to stay alive?

05:07.440 --> 05:08.310
Miyu.

05:09.440 --> 05:10.910
I beg you.

05:10.930 --> 05:12.510
Please go persuade him.

05:12.950 --> 05:14.350
He always listens to you.

05:14.660 --> 05:16.320
You are the one he loves the most.

05:16.320 --> 05:17.720
If it weren't for that...

05:25.270 --> 05:27.270
For the sake of your past marriage,

05:28.830 --> 05:30.430
please help him out

05:31.270 --> 05:33.120
and persuade him to keep living.

05:36.720 --> 05:37.600
I'm sorry.

05:40.840 --> 05:43.250
My relationship with Nie Yucheng is over.

05:44.210 --> 05:46.470
I don't want to disturb his life anymore.

05:47.800 --> 05:48.990
Besides,

05:49.270 --> 05:52.040
what he needs the most right now
is inner peace,

05:52.870 --> 05:55.000
not another emotional entanglement.

05:56.140 --> 06:05.370
[Inpatient Building]

05:56.940 --> 05:57.690
If

05:57.720 --> 05:59.500
you really want to persuade him,

05:59.500 --> 06:00.620
you can tell him

06:00.650 --> 06:01.510
in this world,

06:01.510 --> 06:03.430
there are more important things
than his despair

06:03.430 --> 06:04.890
that he needs to shoulder.

06:05.520 --> 06:06.560
His family,

06:06.860 --> 06:07.820
parents

06:08.310 --> 06:09.220
and child.

06:10.310 --> 06:11.080
I think

06:11.420 --> 06:13.220
he can definitely figure it out.

06:18.750 --> 06:22.550
[North Entrance]

06:35.080 --> 06:36.090
Miyu.

07:02.680 --> 07:04.430
♪ A flicker of dim light ♪

07:06.190 --> 07:07.760
♪ A bowl of warm soup ♪

07:10.040 --> 07:11.820
♪ People in the city ♪

07:12.780 --> 07:15.720
♪ Squeezing into the hustle and bustle ♪

07:17.650 --> 07:19.460
♪ The palms of time ♪

07:21.380 --> 07:24.420
♪ Grinding away the simple days ♪

07:25.110 --> 07:27.640
♪ Sprinkling them into this busy world ♪

07:29.050 --> 07:31.220
♪ To be tasted, bit by bit ♪

07:32.810 --> 07:35.860
♪ Embracing this radiant world ♪

07:32.880 --> 07:34.040
Bear it for a moment.

07:35.520 --> 07:36.520
My husband

07:36.340 --> 07:39.370
♪ Keeps the heart from fading to grey ♪

07:36.540 --> 07:39.940
is the most handsome,
even more handsome than an Arab prince.

07:39.960 --> 07:43.080
♪ Life's joy, sorrow, cold, and warmth ♪

07:43.820 --> 07:46.440
♪ Intertwined within the mundane ♪

07:47.860 --> 07:51.050
♪ Let us bravely gather up ♪

07:51.720 --> 07:55.170
♪ The forgotten past ♪

07:54.500 --> 07:55.810
From now on,

07:56.080 --> 07:58.350
♪ There may be regrets ♪

07:56.650 --> 07:58.650
I won't let you get hurt.

07:59.100 --> 08:00.720
I'll protect you forever.

08:00.010 --> 08:02.190
♪ There may be loneliness ♪

08:02.000 --> 08:04.060
And I'll protect our family forever.

08:06.080 --> 08:07.350
I swear.

08:13.920 --> 08:15.240
Nurse.

08:17.650 --> 08:18.830
I want to eat.

08:32.299 --> 08:35.780
♪ Embracing this radiant world ♪

08:36.200 --> 08:39.320
♪ Keeps the heart from fading to grey ♪

08:39.200 --> 08:40.409
Hello, Mr. Su.

08:39.809 --> 08:43.130
♪ Life's joy, sorrow, cold, and warmth ♪

08:40.440 --> 08:42.130
The verdict is out.

08:42.159 --> 08:43.270
We won the case.

08:43.669 --> 08:46.310
♪ Intertwined within the mundane ♪

08:47.710 --> 08:51.010
♪ Let us bravely gather up ♪

08:47.990 --> 08:49.310
Thanks for your hard work, Mr. Su.

08:49.310 --> 08:50.460
But there's a situation.

08:50.460 --> 08:51.940
You need to be mentally prepared first.

08:51.580 --> 08:55.000
♪ The forgotten past ♪

08:51.960 --> 08:54.010
Mr. Nie has said that

08:54.080 --> 08:56.240
he can't come up with that much money
for the time being.

08:56.240 --> 08:57.650
He has applied for a stay of execution.

08:57.650 --> 08:58.570
I got it.

08:57.840 --> 09:00.510
♪ Walking through this world ♪

08:59.840 --> 09:02.230
Let him
get through this difficult time first.

09:02.230 --> 09:06.340
♪ Leaving no regrets behind ♪

09:02.640 --> 09:04.310
I'm not in a hurry to use this money.

09:04.310 --> 09:05.310
Understood.

09:06.290 --> 09:07.600
Thank you so much

09:07.620 --> 09:09.310
for this period of time, Mr. Su.

09:09.310 --> 09:10.880
You're welcome.

09:10.910 --> 09:12.710
I'm glad my client is satisfied.

09:38.490 --> 09:41.760
[Budget Sheet
of Yuntian Group Bidding Meeting]

09:41.790 --> 09:46.920
[Marketing Campaign Expenses]
[Advertising Fees] [Other Items]

09:50.600 --> 09:53.570
[Signature of the Person in Charge,
Ji Feng]

10:02.350 --> 10:04.110
Are you still at the hotel?

10:04.200 --> 10:04.540
[Release to send]

10:04.690 --> 10:06.130
[Xu Miyu]

10:06.150 --> 10:07.200
[Typing...]

10:09.960 --> 10:13.210
[Xu Miyu]

10:13.400 --> 10:14.510
I'm already off work.

10:14.510 --> 10:15.770
I'm outside right now.

10:15.800 --> 10:16.860
What's the matter?

10:21.300 --> 10:22.540
Where are you going?

10:22.660 --> 10:24.090
[Release to send]

10:26.910 --> 10:27.110
[Release to cancel]

10:27.150 --> 10:28.150
[Xu Miyu]

10:43.870 --> 10:45.250
Ask someone from your department

10:45.250 --> 10:47.710
to come to my office
and fetch the documents.

10:49.550 --> 10:52.310
Okay.
I'll send someone over there right away.

11:08.210 --> 11:15.950
[TAN's Art]

11:26.790 --> 11:28.650
I just had a feeling you'd be here.

11:28.770 --> 11:29.720
Welcome.

11:29.750 --> 11:32.200
I missed your opening ceremony previously,

11:32.200 --> 11:33.890
so I didn't get to tell you—

11:33.920 --> 11:34.790
Congratulations!

11:34.790 --> 11:36.730
You finally have your own gallery.

11:36.760 --> 11:38.140
Alright. Don't stand on ceremony.

11:38.140 --> 11:38.780
Come on in.

11:39.970 --> 11:44.580
[TAN's Art]

11:52.640 --> 11:53.720
Just make a comment.

11:53.720 --> 11:54.760
What do you think?

11:57.020 --> 11:58.620
This is your style,

11:58.680 --> 12:01.150
being both free and bold.

12:01.910 --> 12:03.480
Alright. You still know me the best.

12:03.480 --> 12:04.010
Let's go.

12:09.780 --> 12:11.510
The downstairs is your gallery

12:11.550 --> 12:13.910
while the upstairs is your studio.

12:15.480 --> 12:16.670
When I'm free,

12:16.670 --> 12:17.960
I often visit galleries

12:17.960 --> 12:19.600
and art museums,

12:19.620 --> 12:21.000
but I rarely have the chance

12:21.000 --> 12:23.650
to see an artist's studio
with my own eyes.

12:23.680 --> 12:25.910
Today,
it's like making my dream come true.

12:25.910 --> 12:27.310
Feel free to look around.

12:31.360 --> 12:32.820
Can I touch these?

12:32.940 --> 12:35.670
As long as you don't mind,
feel free to touch them.

12:40.080 --> 12:41.570
The paint is still wet.

12:44.770 --> 12:45.930
What is this?

12:45.960 --> 12:48.440
Is it a work you're trying to creat?

12:50.490 --> 12:51.420
Sort of.

12:52.720 --> 12:54.000
May I have the honor

12:54.030 --> 12:55.360
to be its first viewer?

12:59.400 --> 13:00.200
I'm sorry.

13:00.200 --> 13:00.960
If it's inconvenient...

13:00.960 --> 13:01.760
You can see it.

13:05.440 --> 13:06.440
Okay. Alright.

13:47.590 --> 13:48.700
I originally wanted to

13:48.700 --> 13:51.480
frame it before giving it to you.

13:51.750 --> 13:52.630
Now that...

13:54.270 --> 13:55.080
Okay.

13:55.480 --> 13:56.690
Mr. Tan, I...

13:56.710 --> 13:58.240
Please don't have any pressure.

13:58.240 --> 14:00.240
You helped me
organize the art exhibition so well.

14:00.240 --> 14:02.040
Consider this a thank-you gift.

14:02.200 --> 14:03.660
It's sincere enough, huh?

14:09.260 --> 14:10.200
Thank you.

14:10.960 --> 14:12.690
I like this painting very much.

14:13.730 --> 14:16.130
Actually,
I should be the one thanking you.

14:17.350 --> 14:18.920
Every creator

14:18.940 --> 14:21.670
longs for someone
who can naturally inspire him.

14:22.200 --> 14:23.320
Having met you

14:24.320 --> 14:25.730
is actually my luck.

14:50.910 --> 14:52.910
The Golden Wutong District

14:53.140 --> 14:55.230
is the core area of culture and art.

14:55.410 --> 14:57.540
It suits your temperament perfectly.

14:57.820 --> 15:00.310
Things will definitely
get better and better here.

15:00.310 --> 15:01.710
I'm really happy for you.

15:03.590 --> 15:05.200
Why don't you ask me

15:05.220 --> 15:08.150
why I'm staying in Shanghai
for future development?

15:12.620 --> 15:15.610
This is an ideal place for creators.

15:17.100 --> 15:18.090
Well said.

15:23.120 --> 15:26.900
♪ Love is truly not easy to obtain ♪

15:23.230 --> 15:24.760
The more I look at this city,

15:24.870 --> 15:26.080
the more I like it.

15:28.350 --> 15:29.050
Really.

15:30.500 --> 15:34.200
♪ I can't hold on to you
if you want to leave ♪

15:37.470 --> 15:41.430
♪ I tell myself I'm not hurt
once things settle down ♪

15:45.110 --> 15:49.010
♪ But I realize I can't deceive myself ♪

15:52.470 --> 15:56.220
♪ But I've already started living
like I'm not myself anymore ♪

15:59.900 --> 16:02.780
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

16:06.120 --> 16:11.970
♪ I feel reluctant to recall
or forget those memories ♪

16:14.460 --> 16:17.690
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

16:21.070 --> 16:26.790
♪ I feel reluctant to grab on to you,
and I can't breathe ♪

16:27.970 --> 16:30.830
♪ I've been indulging myself ♪

16:30.930 --> 16:36.050
[My Dear Pearl]

16:51.860 --> 16:53.500
[Yuntian Group,
China Resources Financial Building]

16:53.520 --> 16:54.750
[Project Bidding Meeting]

16:54.890 --> 16:55.740
[China Resources Financial Building,
A Landmark in the City]

16:55.770 --> 16:56.800
[Yuntian Group Invites You
to Build Brilliance Together]

16:56.900 --> 17:00.240
[Fengze Construction]

17:00.330 --> 17:01.220
[Bocheng Construction]

17:08.540 --> 17:09.520
[Xingyao Construction] [Liberty Group]

17:17.920 --> 17:19.750
Hello, Mr. Ji.

17:20.910 --> 17:22.079
Hello, Mr. Ji.

17:22.640 --> 17:23.740
Hello, Mr. Ji.

17:43.370 --> 17:45.090
Welcome, Mr. Lin.

17:45.120 --> 17:46.770
I'm Ji Feng, the general manager here.

17:46.770 --> 17:47.280
Please come in.

17:47.280 --> 17:47.660
Okay.

17:50.580 --> 17:51.370
Hello, everyone.

17:51.370 --> 17:53.380
This way, please.

17:53.620 --> 17:54.350
Hello.

17:54.380 --> 17:55.020
Please come in.

17:55.020 --> 17:56.220
So this is your hotel?

17:56.640 --> 17:57.220
Yes.

18:07.560 --> 18:08.690
Thanks, Wei.

18:09.660 --> 18:11.240
Alright. See you later then.

18:11.240 --> 18:12.350
Okay.

18:13.480 --> 18:14.000
See you later.

18:14.000 --> 18:14.860
Hello, Mr. Wei.

18:33.060 --> 18:33.830
Hello.

18:33.860 --> 18:35.070
Ms. Xu, please come in.

18:35.070 --> 18:36.030
Okay. Thanks.

18:39.440 --> 18:40.640
Mr. Yang.

18:42.290 --> 18:43.530
Ms. Xu.

18:43.640 --> 18:44.680
We've met again.

18:45.570 --> 18:47.130
I've heard this time,

18:47.160 --> 18:48.310
you are already

18:48.340 --> 18:49.540
the sales manager.

18:49.680 --> 18:50.370
Yes.

18:50.980 --> 18:51.940
Congratulations.

18:51.940 --> 18:52.590
Thank you.

18:53.240 --> 18:55.160
Welcome back to Purong Hotel,

18:55.180 --> 18:57.700
and welcome to the bidding meeting.

18:57.730 --> 18:58.990
On behalf of the sales department,

18:58.990 --> 19:00.150
I'm giving this small gift to you.

19:00.150 --> 19:01.790
It's nothing much, but please accept it.

19:01.790 --> 19:02.870
Thank you.

19:04.050 --> 19:05.380
The food is ready.

19:05.410 --> 19:07.160
I'll take you to the Chinese Restaurant
for a meal.

19:07.160 --> 19:08.150
That's great.

19:08.180 --> 19:10.340
I really miss the food at Purong.

19:10.670 --> 19:11.310
Wait a moment for me.

19:11.310 --> 19:12.160
I'm going to get changed.

19:12.160 --> 19:13.620
I'll wait for you outside.

19:48.690 --> 19:49.650
Wait!

19:55.820 --> 19:56.990
Ms. Xu.

19:57.670 --> 19:58.650
You must be a newcomer.

19:58.650 --> 19:59.720
I've never seen you before.

19:59.720 --> 20:00.970
My name is Dai Hui.

20:01.290 --> 20:02.360
Don't be nervous.

20:02.380 --> 20:04.060
Everyone tends to make mistakes at first.

20:04.060 --> 20:04.690
It's fine.

20:05.910 --> 20:06.920
Have a candy.

20:06.950 --> 20:08.280
Thank you, Ms. Xu.

20:08.850 --> 20:09.640
Ms. Xu.

20:10.520 --> 20:11.570
Sorry to keep you waiting.

20:11.570 --> 20:12.250
This way, please.

20:12.250 --> 20:13.030
Let's go.

20:22.300 --> 20:23.310
I'm sorry, Mr. Marcos.

20:23.310 --> 20:25.440
It's fine, Ms. Xu. Just leave it there.

20:25.550 --> 20:27.320
Although I'm allergic to pollen,

20:27.320 --> 20:29.340
I'll be fine in a spacious place like this

20:29.340 --> 20:30.770
for a short while.

20:30.930 --> 20:31.580
But...

20:31.610 --> 20:32.330
It's fine.

20:33.070 --> 20:35.670
I usually can't have flowers in my room,

20:36.000 --> 20:36.720
so,

20:37.030 --> 20:39.970
occasionally seeing them outside
puts me in a good mood.

20:39.970 --> 20:41.720
What's more, don't deprive everyone

20:41.720 --> 20:44.320
of the chance to see flowers
just because of me.

20:45.220 --> 20:46.380
How about this?

20:46.410 --> 20:47.880
Later, I'll put some silk flowers

20:47.880 --> 20:49.080
in your room.

20:49.220 --> 20:51.090
That would be great. Thank you.

20:51.110 --> 20:52.020
Please.

20:55.090 --> 20:55.650
Please.

20:57.820 --> 20:58.670
Wait!

21:01.700 --> 21:02.460
Boss.

21:05.170 --> 21:06.650
Isn't this Mr. Marcos

21:06.680 --> 21:08.010
from the Liberty Group?

21:09.370 --> 21:10.340
Hello.

21:24.460 --> 21:25.630
Mr. Niu, this way, please.

21:25.630 --> 21:26.190
Okay.

21:27.550 --> 21:28.360
See you later.

21:31.850 --> 21:32.840
Please come in.

21:36.100 --> 21:36.810
Thank you.

21:39.850 --> 21:40.930
Give it to me.

21:41.560 --> 21:42.550
His assistant seems to be

21:42.550 --> 21:44.880
someone who left our company previously.

21:47.480 --> 21:48.270
Marcos,

21:48.270 --> 21:50.330
is there anything I can help you with?

21:51.060 --> 21:52.130
Well,

21:52.150 --> 21:54.110
the assistant to the president
of Jinkun Group

21:54.110 --> 21:56.650
came from our company.

21:57.210 --> 21:58.160
Three years ago,

21:58.160 --> 21:59.400
he was fired

21:59.400 --> 22:01.000
due to some misconduct.

22:01.450 --> 22:02.660
Maybe we're judging

22:02.680 --> 22:05.010
others by our own standards improperly.

22:05.040 --> 22:07.120
Also, Jinkun Group's reputation

22:07.140 --> 22:09.200
in the industry is quite divided.

22:09.220 --> 22:10.380
Now that I've run into him today,

22:10.380 --> 22:11.140
I just

22:11.620 --> 22:12.880
have to keep an eye out.

22:12.900 --> 22:13.880
Don't worry.

22:13.900 --> 22:15.280
I will tell all departments

22:15.280 --> 22:17.000
to strengthen the measures
on information security management.

22:17.000 --> 22:18.490
I really appreciate your help.

22:18.490 --> 22:19.290
Thank you.

22:29.200 --> 22:31.330
Are you sure you really want to do this?

22:31.510 --> 22:33.940
This is what we agreed on
from the very beginning.

22:33.940 --> 22:35.620
My demands are quite simple.

22:35.650 --> 22:37.560
Either you help me
find out about the base price,

22:37.560 --> 22:38.280
or

22:38.310 --> 22:39.170
you help me find out about

22:39.170 --> 22:40.830
Liberty Group's bid price.

22:41.290 --> 22:43.800
Well, how can this work?

22:46.060 --> 22:47.160
Why didn't you knock on the door
before coming in?

22:47.160 --> 22:48.070
How rude.

22:48.250 --> 22:49.210
I'm sorry, Mr. Wei.

22:49.210 --> 22:49.970
Just get out.

22:55.460 --> 22:57.130
As the saying goes,

22:57.150 --> 22:59.350
"Great wealth comes with great risks."

22:59.920 --> 23:01.850
As long as you put this small device

23:01.900 --> 23:04.300
in Marcos' room secretly,

23:04.320 --> 23:05.780
by doing it just like that,

23:06.430 --> 23:08.290
you'll get 5 million yuan easily.

23:08.300 --> 23:09.020
Bro,

23:09.400 --> 23:10.600
I treat you well, don't I?

23:10.600 --> 23:11.820
Mr. Niu,

23:11.850 --> 23:13.850
this is not a small matter.

23:13.990 --> 23:15.340
The bidding meeting for the skyscraper

23:15.340 --> 23:16.790
involves funds of billions of yuan.

23:16.790 --> 23:17.720
The risk I'm taking

23:17.720 --> 23:19.920
does not match up with the reward.

23:20.240 --> 23:21.810
What are you talking about?

23:23.000 --> 23:24.720
This grand hotel is yours.

23:24.960 --> 23:26.420
These are all your people.

23:27.000 --> 23:29.060
What risks will you even have to take?

23:29.930 --> 23:32.190
Don't you know my current situation?

23:32.280 --> 23:33.480
That old madam above me

23:33.480 --> 23:35.450
won't tolerate any misconduct.

23:35.710 --> 23:37.240
An ambitious guy
has also come from outside,

23:37.240 --> 23:38.530
trying to overthrow me.

23:38.530 --> 23:40.690
I have an insatiable wife at home, too.

23:40.950 --> 23:44.350
How long can I live on the 5 million yuan
you're offering to me?

23:47.460 --> 23:48.660
Then give me a number.

23:51.440 --> 23:52.570
20 million yuan.

23:52.800 --> 23:54.360
Pay 10% of it first.

23:56.510 --> 23:58.510
You haven't done anything yet,

23:58.510 --> 23:59.900
and you're asking me for 2 million yuan?

23:59.900 --> 24:00.720
On what grounds can you do that,

24:00.720 --> 24:01.550
dude?

24:02.650 --> 24:04.260
Because we're friends.

24:05.430 --> 24:07.150
You wouldn't just use me, your buddy,

24:07.150 --> 24:08.810
like a credit card, would you?

24:10.170 --> 24:11.720
If you don't want to do that,
just forget it.

24:11.720 --> 24:13.130
Just pretend I didn't say it.

24:13.130 --> 24:14.610
Let's eat. It tastes good.

24:14.640 --> 24:15.510
Come on.

24:16.750 --> 24:17.550
Deal.

24:21.380 --> 24:23.300
That's more like it, Mr. Niu.

24:23.330 --> 24:25.120
Come on. Cheers.

24:25.150 --> 24:26.610
You're really something.

24:31.980 --> 24:32.930
Eat.

24:33.310 --> 24:41.770
[Director's Office]

24:33.720 --> 24:34.790
Don't you think

24:34.790 --> 24:36.990
we need to change our mindset this time?

24:41.240 --> 24:41.720
As for the fact that

24:41.720 --> 24:43.480
Yuntian Group's bidding meeting

24:43.480 --> 24:45.150
can be held at Purong this time,

24:45.150 --> 24:47.400
I think it's all thanks to Ms. Xu.

24:47.420 --> 24:49.660
She is indeed a rare talent.

24:49.960 --> 24:52.960
I'm wondering if we could promote her

24:52.960 --> 24:54.020
to be my aide later.

24:54.040 --> 24:55.510
I believe next year's sales volume

24:55.510 --> 24:57.510
will reach new heights.

24:57.960 --> 25:00.160
Actually, Mr. Ji has the same plan, too.

25:00.170 --> 25:02.130
The HR department
has already been informed.

25:02.130 --> 25:04.700
After this bidding
is conducted successfully,

25:04.700 --> 25:07.330
the sales department
will be entrusted to you two.

25:07.330 --> 25:07.980
Okay.

25:10.060 --> 25:12.600
[Director's Office]

25:15.150 --> 25:22.220
[Purong Hotel]

25:15.420 --> 25:16.620
I know what I'm doing.

25:17.920 --> 25:19.250
I'll contact you later.

25:20.240 --> 25:22.770
Mr. Wei,
I need to discuss something with you.

25:23.830 --> 25:24.550
What is it?

25:24.550 --> 25:25.770
Think of a way quickly

25:25.790 --> 25:28.650
to help me drive Xu Miyu
out of the sales department.

25:29.100 --> 25:30.580
Why are you suddenly saying this?

25:30.580 --> 25:32.370
I've been promoted to this position
for just a few days.

25:32.370 --> 25:34.820
She has already teamed up
with the new director

25:34.820 --> 25:37.020
and tried every possible means
to undermine me.

25:37.020 --> 25:38.960
They want to use the performance
of this bidding meeting

25:38.960 --> 25:40.270
to edge me out of my position

25:40.270 --> 25:41.190
as vice director.

25:41.190 --> 25:42.740
This is not like your style.

25:43.350 --> 25:45.460
If you sit firmly in your position,

25:45.490 --> 25:47.150
can anyone remove you from it?

25:47.440 --> 25:48.960
Anyway, if I get edged out,

25:48.980 --> 25:51.240
then no one can help you with your things.

25:52.790 --> 25:53.700
Zhenzhen.

25:54.720 --> 25:56.640
You need to be more understanding.

25:56.640 --> 25:59.350
Ji Feng is now competing with me
in the sales department.

25:59.350 --> 26:01.520
It's inevitable
that these things will happen.

26:01.520 --> 26:02.800
Just put up with it.

26:03.030 --> 26:05.130
There will be more opportunities later,
won't there?

26:05.130 --> 26:06.160
Besides, I'm not anxious yet,

26:06.160 --> 26:07.820
so what are you anxious about?

26:08.100 --> 26:09.310
Wei Siyuan.

26:09.420 --> 26:12.330
You always make your statement
sound so nice every time,

26:12.330 --> 26:15.060
but you've never
fulfilled any of your promises.

26:15.360 --> 26:17.360
My patience is limited.

26:29.130 --> 26:29.940
Wait a moment.

26:56.570 --> 26:57.550
Find a way

26:57.550 --> 26:58.310
to put this stuff

26:58.310 --> 27:00.460
in the room of the Liberty Group's boss.

27:00.460 --> 27:02.000
If you get this done,

27:02.810 --> 27:04.190
I will give you 5 million yuan.

27:04.190 --> 27:06.190
Also, I will promote you

27:06.230 --> 27:07.640
to director officially.

27:08.010 --> 27:09.010
What do you think?

27:13.830 --> 27:14.790
The business
discussed at this bidding meeting

27:14.790 --> 27:16.130
is worth hundreds of millions of yuan.

27:16.130 --> 27:17.930
Doing this is too risky.

27:18.200 --> 27:19.660
I might be put into prison.

27:20.330 --> 27:21.290
Zhenzhen.

27:22.130 --> 27:24.390
Since when have you become such a coward?

27:24.840 --> 27:27.380
High risks bring high rewards.

27:27.680 --> 27:29.340
Don't you want your benefits?

27:29.490 --> 27:31.220
Don't you have a child to raise?

27:35.870 --> 27:37.110
Wei Siyuan.

27:37.920 --> 27:39.190
You've long made up your mind

27:39.190 --> 27:41.060
to ask me to do this for you.

27:41.510 --> 27:42.640
Honestly speaking,

27:43.570 --> 27:44.730
I can't trust

27:44.750 --> 27:46.800
or rely on anyone else.

27:47.610 --> 27:48.740
It has to be you only.

27:53.180 --> 27:53.940
Okay.

27:54.780 --> 27:56.010
For my child's sake,

27:56.300 --> 27:58.830
I can help you
plant the listening device there.

27:58.830 --> 28:00.220
But I have a condition.

28:00.860 --> 28:02.610
5 million yuan is too little.

28:03.370 --> 28:05.160
I want 8 million yuan.

28:05.290 --> 28:07.820
I want to be paid
immediately after it's done.

28:12.310 --> 28:13.440
This is more like you,

28:13.440 --> 28:14.720
Lu Zhenzhen.

28:15.070 --> 28:16.140
8 million yuan.

28:16.920 --> 28:17.530
Okay.

28:18.110 --> 28:20.430
I'll just give you 8 million yuan. Deal.

28:46.960 --> 28:48.050
Here you are.

28:48.910 --> 28:49.970
Ms. Xu.

28:50.090 --> 28:52.420
Are you going to
give these to the clients?

28:52.590 --> 28:53.920
These are prepared for the guests

28:53.920 --> 28:54.790
who attend the bidding meeting.

28:54.790 --> 28:56.530
I'll deliver them to their rooms later.

28:56.530 --> 28:58.000
Do you need my help?

28:58.020 --> 28:59.760
It's fine. I can go by myself.

28:59.790 --> 29:00.580
Okay.

29:17.160 --> 29:18.360
Miyu.

29:18.610 --> 29:19.760
Why are you here?

29:20.580 --> 29:22.130
I'm here to deliver something to Mr. Yang.

29:22.130 --> 29:22.830
Is he in his room?

29:22.830 --> 29:25.030
I just saw him go out with his assistant.

29:25.480 --> 29:27.810
Well...
I'll wait here for him for a while.

29:28.460 --> 29:29.720
He just went out a moment ago.

29:29.720 --> 29:31.300
I also don't know when he'll be back.

29:31.300 --> 29:32.530
Let me open the door for you first.

29:32.530 --> 29:34.360
You're delivering something
to the guest anyway.

29:34.360 --> 29:34.970
Thank you.

29:37.880 --> 29:38.960
Ms. Xu, Xiang.

29:38.990 --> 29:40.600
This guest needs to check in.

29:41.600 --> 29:43.010
Then how about going by yourself?

29:43.010 --> 29:44.700
Just return the room card to me later.

29:44.700 --> 29:46.230
I'll be back in two minutes.

29:46.510 --> 29:48.770
Come this way
and let me help you check in.

29:51.110 --> 29:52.500
Please show your ID.

29:57.090 --> 29:57.810
Dai.

29:58.400 --> 29:59.230
Ms. Xu.

29:59.550 --> 30:00.700
Why are you here?

30:00.830 --> 30:01.790
I need to go to Room 1822

30:01.790 --> 30:03.050
to deliver something.

30:03.200 --> 30:03.930
Are you okay?

30:04.280 --> 30:04.810
I'm fine.

30:04.850 --> 30:06.090
I'll pick them up with you together.

30:06.090 --> 30:07.090
Thank you, Ms. Xu.

30:58.500 --> 31:00.480
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

31:05.790 --> 31:06.510
M-Miyu.

31:06.510 --> 31:07.590
You're back.

31:10.960 --> 31:12.000
Why are you here?

31:13.170 --> 31:13.890
Well,

31:13.920 --> 31:15.110
I've brought you some

31:15.110 --> 31:16.750
hometown specialities.

31:16.750 --> 31:18.330
Mom and Dad
asked me to bring them here for you.

31:18.330 --> 31:20.290
Look. There's also your favorite

31:20.320 --> 31:21.480
dried fish here.

31:27.800 --> 31:28.630
Um...

31:30.250 --> 31:32.720
I had a bad attitude last time.

31:33.170 --> 31:34.580
I'm sorry.

31:34.610 --> 31:36.850
Mom and Dad scolded me when I went back.

31:37.790 --> 31:39.460
Actually, I came here this time

31:39.460 --> 31:42.180
just to sincerely apologize to you.

31:42.830 --> 31:43.790
Really, Miyu.

31:46.250 --> 31:47.490
It's my fault.

31:52.160 --> 31:54.970
I've quit my job in Shanghai, too.

31:58.310 --> 31:59.160
Well,

31:59.570 --> 32:01.920
Mom and Dad are getting older,
aren't they?

32:01.920 --> 32:03.380
I just want to go back

32:03.400 --> 32:05.680
and help them with the guesthouse.

32:06.780 --> 32:09.060
So... What about Man?

32:09.220 --> 32:10.690
Is he still going to
the international school?

32:10.690 --> 32:11.650
No.

32:11.730 --> 32:13.400
He went back with me.

32:13.430 --> 32:15.930
He's studying in the primary school
in our town now.

32:15.930 --> 32:16.930
It's pretty good.

32:23.470 --> 32:24.540
Um...

32:26.160 --> 32:29.120
I'll just put this stuff here for you.

32:29.140 --> 32:30.470
Don't forget to take it.

32:33.200 --> 32:34.330
Have you eaten yet?

32:34.800 --> 32:36.370
N-Not yet.

32:43.110 --> 32:44.480
It smells so good.

32:47.880 --> 32:48.840
Miyu,

32:49.040 --> 32:51.110
right now, I just want to

32:51.110 --> 32:53.640
help Mom and Dad
run the guesthouse properly.

32:53.690 --> 32:55.370
You're experienced and knowledgeable.

32:55.370 --> 32:56.850
Can you give me some advice

32:56.870 --> 32:59.830
and tell me if there are any tricks?

33:04.970 --> 33:06.630
There are indeed some tricks.

33:12.920 --> 33:14.010
This book

33:14.030 --> 33:16.380
is specifically about
hotels and guesthouses.

33:16.380 --> 33:17.510
There are many cases in it.

33:17.510 --> 33:18.970
Just see if it can help you.

33:20.780 --> 33:21.770
Do you think

33:22.060 --> 33:23.830
this feels like the old days
when we were doing homework

33:23.830 --> 33:25.160
together as kids?

33:25.160 --> 33:27.520
You'd explain the exercises to me,
but I still couldn't understand.

33:27.520 --> 33:29.010
I didn't take it seriously back then.

33:29.010 --> 33:30.170
But now I know

33:30.200 --> 33:31.240
studying is good.

33:31.260 --> 33:32.260
It really is good.

33:33.020 --> 33:34.640
It's not too late for you to study now.

33:34.640 --> 33:36.220
It's never too late to study.

33:36.220 --> 33:38.530
Right. And I wouldn't dare not to study.

33:38.550 --> 33:41.290
Otherwise, I can't even tutor Man
in his homework.

33:41.290 --> 33:42.680
You know what? His homework

33:42.680 --> 33:45.010
is much harder than that in our childhood.

33:45.550 --> 33:47.440
Look. I'm digressing again.

33:48.000 --> 33:48.810
Could you

33:48.830 --> 33:51.590
recommend more books like this to me?

33:52.020 --> 33:54.300
The Internet is so advanced now.

33:54.320 --> 33:56.170
You can just search online.

33:56.400 --> 33:57.920
I did search online.

33:57.940 --> 34:00.050
When I searched "guesthouse",

34:00.080 --> 34:01.440
there would be many travel ads

34:01.440 --> 34:03.790
popping up on the Internet.

34:05.210 --> 34:06.210
Actually,

34:06.510 --> 34:07.680
you need to figure out

34:07.680 --> 34:08.670
what exactly you want to search for.

34:08.670 --> 34:10.920
For example, do you want to
search for guesthouse management

34:10.920 --> 34:12.949
or guesthouse operation cases?

34:12.969 --> 34:14.590
Enter these keywords

34:14.590 --> 34:15.850
and give it a try again.

34:15.949 --> 34:17.210
You're still the best.

34:17.250 --> 34:19.110
Where can I search for such content?

34:19.110 --> 34:19.960
Please teach me.

34:19.960 --> 34:22.110
Explain it to me in detail. I...

34:24.590 --> 34:25.800
Am I too stupid?

34:25.800 --> 34:27.600
I don't know how to do this at all.

34:28.230 --> 34:28.760
Here.

34:28.760 --> 34:30.290
I really need to study more.

34:30.980 --> 34:31.989
Look at this app.

34:32.710 --> 34:34.150
Just type in

34:34.150 --> 34:37.989
"guesthouse operation cases."

34:38.020 --> 34:39.690
See? Didn't they all pop up?

34:40.190 --> 34:41.719
Take a look yourself first.

34:45.120 --> 34:46.510
It smells so good.

34:53.270 --> 34:57.540
[Sign-in Desk]

34:53.850 --> 34:55.500
Please sign in over here.

34:57.620 --> 34:59.620
[Yuntian Group's Bidding Meeting
for China Resources Financial Building]

34:57.760 --> 34:58.940
Ladies and gentlemen,

34:58.940 --> 35:00.760
the bidding meeting is about to start.
Please come in.

34:59.630 --> 35:00.810
[Invites You to Witness it Together]

35:00.900 --> 35:06.410
[Bidding Meeting]

35:02.280 --> 35:03.240
Please come in.

35:06.520 --> 35:09.800
[Bidding Meeting]

35:06.760 --> 35:07.920
The bidding meeting is about to start.

35:07.920 --> 35:09.890
Everyone,
please come in and take your seats.

35:09.890 --> 35:11.470
[Yuntian Group's Bidding Meeting
for China Resources Financial Building]

35:11.490 --> 35:12.470
[Invites You to Witness it Together]

35:12.540 --> 35:16.050
[Bidding Meeting]

35:18.100 --> 35:20.180
Respected leaders and guests,

35:20.200 --> 35:21.150
regarding Yuntian Group's

35:21.150 --> 35:23.320
procurement bidding for the Project
of China Resources Financial Building,

35:23.320 --> 35:24.960
there are totally 162 companies

35:24.960 --> 35:25.900
participating in the bidding.

35:25.900 --> 35:27.220
They are...

35:27.240 --> 35:28.610
Liberty Group,

35:29.000 --> 35:30.350
Jinkun Group,

35:30.560 --> 35:31.920
Fuchun Group,

35:30.630 --> 35:35.660
[Fengze Construction]
[Bocheng Construction]

35:32.210 --> 35:33.520
Lianhe Construction,

35:33.550 --> 35:34.810
Fengze Construction,

35:34.840 --> 35:36.230
Bocheng Construction,

35:36.370 --> 35:37.680
Hengtai Construction,

35:37.680 --> 35:39.110
Zhuoyuan Construction,

35:39.130 --> 35:40.650
Xingyao Construction,

35:40.720 --> 35:42.660
Lvzhu Ecological Environment,

35:43.210 --> 35:45.230
Zhijian Engineering Technology,

35:45.420 --> 35:46.840
Ruida Construction,

35:46.890 --> 35:48.200
Weiye Engineering...

35:49.810 --> 35:51.190
The list of the companies having lunch

35:51.190 --> 35:53.100
at the Chinese Restaurant
has been finalized.

35:53.100 --> 35:54.030
Go print 5 copies

35:54.050 --> 35:55.560
and give them to the kitchen staff.

35:55.560 --> 35:57.750
Tell the kitchen to prepare meals
according to the headcount.

35:57.750 --> 35:58.540
Okay.

36:16.650 --> 36:17.380
Next, we'd like to

36:17.380 --> 36:19.490
ask the notary to unseal
the bidding documents from each company

36:19.490 --> 36:20.700
and keep a record.

36:20.720 --> 36:21.590
If any bidder

36:21.590 --> 36:23.440
has any objections to the bid opening,

36:23.440 --> 36:25.100
please raise them on the spot.

36:25.880 --> 36:27.550
[Bidding Document]

36:41.970 --> 36:42.110
[Bidding Document]

36:44.890 --> 36:46.600
Fengling Group's bid

36:47.110 --> 36:48.920
is 9.417 billion yuan.

36:48.960 --> 36:50.000
The construction period

36:50.000 --> 36:51.430
is 770 days.

36:57.000 --> 36:58.130
Liberty Group's bid

36:58.140 --> 37:01.020
is 8.513 billion yuan.

36:59.180 --> 37:03.270
[Yuntian Group,
China Resources Financial Building]

37:01.050 --> 37:02.070
The construction period

37:02.070 --> 37:03.590
is 684 days.

37:03.750 --> 37:05.070
[Yuntian Group Bidding Meeting]

37:11.030 --> 37:11.910
Mr. Niu.

37:12.510 --> 37:15.040
The hotel says
they don't have any King Crabs.

37:15.820 --> 37:17.680
What kind of crappy hotel is this?

37:18.690 --> 37:20.000
Tell them

37:20.430 --> 37:22.580
Mr. Niu never eats working meals.

37:22.610 --> 37:24.480
Order a King Crab for me alone.

37:24.850 --> 37:25.730
Got it?

37:26.010 --> 37:26.860
Got it.

37:30.210 --> 37:31.740
Jinkun Group's bid

37:31.980 --> 37:33.890
is 8.412 billion yuan.

37:33.920 --> 37:35.150
The construction period

37:35.150 --> 37:36.590
is 680 days.

37:41.730 --> 37:43.910
Now it's time for the Bidding Committee
to evaluate the bids.

37:43.910 --> 37:45.640
Please take a break, everyone.

37:47.540 --> 37:48.940
What are you waiting for?

37:49.020 --> 37:49.750
Just go now.

37:51.020 --> 37:51.540
Okay.

37:51.560 --> 37:52.680
King Crabs!

37:58.070 --> 37:59.440
Everyone, please go to the rest area

37:59.440 --> 38:01.640
and take a rest with some refreshments.

38:01.760 --> 38:02.850
Mr. Niu said

38:03.020 --> 38:04.880
he must have King Crabs for lunch.

38:05.310 --> 38:06.230
Here's the thing.

38:06.230 --> 38:07.480
Didn't I tell you this?

38:07.480 --> 38:09.460
It's not that we refuse to
cook King Crabs for you.

38:09.460 --> 38:10.190
The problem is that our kitchen

38:10.190 --> 38:12.120
really doesn't have any right now.

38:12.240 --> 38:13.400
How about this?

38:13.400 --> 38:15.070
We just got a batch of bluefin tuna,

38:15.070 --> 38:15.960
and we can make sashimi with it.

38:15.960 --> 38:16.920
Is that okay?

38:16.960 --> 38:18.750
You should've said so earlier. We want it.

38:18.750 --> 38:20.280
Then I'll go arrange it now.

38:22.280 --> 38:23.880
There's a listening device!

38:24.130 --> 38:25.730
There's a listening device!

38:27.330 --> 38:28.930
There's a listening device.

38:41.500 --> 38:43.100
Remember to mute your phone.

38:43.150 --> 38:44.480
I'm sorry, Mr. Xue.

38:53.430 --> 38:54.890
Is everything arranged at the restaurant?

38:54.890 --> 38:56.010
Lunch is ready.

38:56.050 --> 38:57.820
The delegates are already eating.

38:57.820 --> 38:58.750
What about here?

38:59.110 --> 38:59.900
We are checking

38:59.900 --> 39:02.810
for devices that are paired
with the listening device.

39:02.810 --> 39:04.850
Could it be an outsider?

39:04.880 --> 39:06.090
It's possible.

39:06.110 --> 39:09.100
The security guards are also checking
the surveillance footage.

39:09.100 --> 39:11.030
Where was the listening device found?

39:11.030 --> 39:12.440
In the vase in this room.

39:12.880 --> 39:14.860
Why is there a vase in Marcos's room?

39:14.860 --> 39:16.260
If we keep failing to pair the devices,

39:16.260 --> 39:17.800
we can only check the surveillance footage

39:17.800 --> 39:19.470
to see who sent the vase there

39:19.500 --> 39:20.620
or once handled it.

39:20.640 --> 39:21.920
How is that possible?

39:21.950 --> 39:23.430
There are only these several people.

39:23.430 --> 39:24.720
Let's test it again.

39:37.470 --> 39:38.620
[Bluetooth Paired Successfully]

39:42.280 --> 39:43.090
Wait.

39:44.760 --> 39:45.720
Mr. Ji.

39:48.000 --> 39:49.630
You said it yourself just now.

39:49.630 --> 39:50.740
Once it's detected,

39:50.740 --> 39:52.030
the person must be taken
to the investigation room.

39:52.030 --> 39:53.380
So many people are watching.

39:53.380 --> 39:55.640
We should at least finish the procedure.

39:58.680 --> 40:01.610
I'll personally take her
to the investigation room.

40:06.710 --> 40:10.020
[Investigation Section]

40:31.880 --> 40:33.110
The vase you just mentioned

40:33.110 --> 40:35.400
was indeed delivered
to Marcos's room by me.

40:35.400 --> 40:37.400
And I was the only one who handled it.

40:37.710 --> 40:38.630
But I really didn't know

40:38.630 --> 40:39.850
there was a listening device inside it.

40:39.850 --> 40:40.440
Nor do I know

40:40.440 --> 40:42.900
why my phone
is successfully paired with it.

40:43.030 --> 40:45.630
The listening device
has nothing to do with me.

40:46.840 --> 40:49.270
Stay here for a while.

40:49.520 --> 40:51.150
I'll aks someone
to bring your coat for you.

40:51.150 --> 40:52.950
It'll be a bit cold here at night.

40:54.480 --> 40:55.600
It really wasn't me.

40:54.580 --> 40:55.900
[Investigation Section]

40:58.850 --> 41:01.190
I know this has nothing to do with you.

41:01.740 --> 41:02.960
Later, someone will come here

41:02.960 --> 41:04.060
to ask you questions.

41:04.060 --> 41:06.260
Just answer the questions truthfully.

41:11.570 --> 41:12.500
Don't be afraid.

41:13.700 --> 41:14.560
You'll be fine.

41:22.410 --> 41:31.230
[Investigation Section]

41:34.790 --> 41:37.570
[Investigation Section]
